<li><em>Hubs&#160;:</em> (<a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="https://share.coursera.org/wiki/images/d/d4/CMAP3%288%29HUBS.jpg">https://share.coursera.org/wiki/images/d/d4/CMAP3%288%29HUBS.jpg</a>)</li>
